>Description:
I'd like to request that DrScheme have some means other 
than using a scrollbar to select the font size. It can be
really really hard to select my font size, and I almost 
never succeed in having the scrollbar stop on the fontsize
I want to select. It would be a lot nicer if there were 
a way to type in the size, possibly in addition to the 
scroll bar
