State-Changed-Why:
    I added two buttons: +1 and -1. Hopefully you can use the slider to get
    close and then do fine adjustments with those buttons.
    
    A text box is a pain, since it is difficult to tell when you are in an 
    intermediate state (ie typing "5" or your way to "52" or if that's the size
    you want) and guess wrong is annoying.
    
    Hope that's okay.
